description._content: Original Collection: Extension and Experiment Station Communications (P 120) Item Number: P120 acc 97:092 Image Description: Esther Taskerud became the Assistant State 4-H Club Leader in November of 1947. Taskerud later served as the head of Home Economics from 1963-1969, retiring in 1970. You can find this image by searching for the item number by clicking here. Want more?
